"```sql\nSELECT c.Score, pl.LinkTypeId\nFROM comments c\nJOIN postLinks pl ON c.PostId = pl.PostId\nWHERE c.PostId = 395;\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the score from the `comments` table and the link type ID from the `postLinks` table for the specified post ID 395. The query uses a JOIN operation to connect the `comments` and `postLinks` tables based on the `PostId` column, which is a foreign key relationship."